data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR DREAM HOME TUCKED AWAY IN A PEACEFUL CUL DE SAC WHERE TRANQUILITY AND CHARM ABOUND. FROM THE MOMENT YOU ARRIVE, YOU'LL BE CAPTIVATED BY THE BEAUTY OF THE ONE LEVEL SANCTUARY. AS YOU APPROACH THE MANICURED LAWN AND WELL MAINTAINED EXTERIOR SET THE STAGE FOR WHAT AWAITS INSIDE. STEP THROUGH THE FRONT DOOR AND BE GREETED BY A WARM AND INVITING ATMOSPHERE OF THE LIVING/SITTING AREA. THE HEART OF THE HOME IS A FAMILY ROOM WITH CATHEDRAL CEILING THAT ADDS AN AIRY AND SPACIOUS FEEL TO THE SPACE. THE KITCHEN IS A CHEF'S DELIGHT, EQUIPPED WITH MODERN APPLIANCES, NEW REFRIGERATOR, AMPLE COUNTER SPACE, AND A CONVENIENT ISLAND THAT SERVES AS A PERFECT SPOT FOR MEAL PREP OR CASUAL DINING. FOR MORE FORMAL GATHERINGS, A SEPARATE DINING ROOM AWAITS. THE MBR SUITE OFFERS LARGE EN SUITE WITH SEPARATE SHOWER AND TUB, DOUBLE VANITY. OUTSIDE, YOUR OWN PRIVATE OASIS AWAITS. THE FENCED BACKYARD IS A PERFECT PLACE TO GROW ORGANIC PRODUCE IN THIS GARDENER'S PARADISE, BOASTING LUSH LANDSCAPING, COLORFUL BLOOMS THIS BACKYARD OFFERS A PEACEFUL RETREAT FOR ALL TO ENJOY MORNING COFFEE OR TEA TAKING IN THE VIEWS OF THE GARDEN. WITH ITS IDEAL LOCATION ON A QUIET CUL DE SAC THIS HOME OFFERS THE PERFECT BLEND OF PRIVACY AND CONVENIENCE.
